 Operational Capability (EOC) and provide the program structure necessary to enable transition into a Program of Record (POR) in accordance with acquisition transformation strategy. POR will continue testing
 thru Initial Operational Capability, a Full Rate Production Decision, and continued P3I enhancements to enable rapid affordable future upgrades to pace the threat and meet key operational problems.

 FY2027 MACE program includes includes $0 of discretionary funding and $156,000 thousand of mandatory (reconciliation) funds for a total of $156,000 thousand FY2027 funding. FY2027 mandatory
 (reconciliation) funding supports the procurement of 353 LOT 1 MACE AURs and associated production engineering, logistics and program management support.

