 control agents and defensive land mines for the Military Sea Lift Command, Naval Criminal Investigate Service (NCIS), Marine and Navy Air-wings, Maritime Force Protection Command, and Naval Expeditionary
 Combat Command.

 Additionally, the Naval Special Warfare (NSW) small arms ammunition program includes (22 -.50 Cal) ammunition required for the organic weapon systems carried by US Navy SEALs, while the various hand
 grenades are employed for force protection, break contact maneuvers, ambushes, and target assaults.$$, $$$$, $$Exhibit P-40, Budget Line Item Justification: PB 2027 Navy                                                                                                                               Date: April 2026
