Description:
The COLUMBIA ELECTRONICS budget funds procurement of the Non-Propulsion Electronics System (NPES), which is the collection of command and control subsystems required to provide all of the non-
strategic warfighting, navigation, communications, and crew information technology functions. The Combat Control P-35 item contains processing electronics and attack center controls and displays required
