procured software applications (Tactical Control, Weapons Control, Common Infrastructure Services, Voyage Management System, Information Assurance, On-Board Team Trainer Master Controller, Integrated
System Maintenance Tool), initial spares, ship systems data, and Combat Control program management labor.

