(2) FY2027/SSBN829 includes procurement and installation of the SWS Fire Control Subsystem equipment suite for the COLUMBIA Class Targeting Engineering Test System (TETS). The TETS is the shore
based installation of the tactical Fire Control System (FCS) maintained onboard a government facility that is used to develop and qualify the targeting and mission planning software for the Strategic Weapon
System (SWS), as well as support problem resolution and investigation of trouble reports received from the fleet. The TETS is required to support COLUMBIA Class Demonstration and Shakedown Availability
(DASO) test events.




